OL,3,CRAF veteran appears in court after
OL,4,Carmed stand-off with police
OL,6,FAn RAF veteran appeared in court on
OL,7,FSaturday accused of a firearms offence
OL,8,Fafter he pointed a "realistic looking"
OL,9,Fimitation gun at armed police
OL,10,Fdemanding to be shot.
OL,12,FDescribed by District Judge Mark
OL,13,FHamill as a case of "suicide by cop,"
OL,14,FBelfast Magistrates Court heard that
OL,15,FPeter Donaldson is lucky to be alive
OL,16,Fas he put officers in such a state of
OL,17,Ffear, they fired several rounds at the
OL,18,F45-year-old during a near two hour
OL,19,Fstand-off.
