OL,3,CRAF veteran appears in court after
OL,4,Carmed stand-off with police
OL,6,FHe told police that having been in the
OL,7,FRAF from 2001 and to 2006 where he
OL,8,Fserved two tours of Iraq, he was
OL,9,Fmedically discharged after suffering a
OL,10,Fback injury of such severity that he
OL,11,Fhas since been on painkillers,
OL,12,Fincluding fentanyl, a plethora of
OL,13,Fmedications.
OL,15,FWhile his doctor had advised him to
OL,16,Fcome off meds slowly, he stopped them
OL,17,Fall because of their side effects and
OL,18,Fhow they make him feel but as the
OL,19,Fweekend progressed "he got
OL,20,Fprogressively worse."
